text: Now abstract liner isn't new — remember the pointillism trend from last year? Or every time Solange leaves the house? But this is one of the first times Jenner has tried something so artsy herself. And we expect to see it a lot more soon, which we're not mad about at all given how it looks easy as hell to recreate ourselves. Like, there's no real formula you have to consider, and no tools you have to use other than the eyeliner and brush. Plus, how long do you think this took to create? According to Phillips, just 10 minutes.
